                     <interp inst="t18240715-109-person995" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to Mr. Goodber, pawnbroker, Paternoster-row, Spitalfields. On the 26th of June, the prisoner pawned two saws.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240715-109-person996">
                  JOSEPH 
                  WALTON
               <interp inst="t18240715-109-person996" type="surname" value="WALTON"></interp>
