                     <interp inst="t18240715-109-person996" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I was talking to Conde, the prisoner came to the door with a saw, and I took him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I met one Norman in Brown's-lane, who sent me to sell the things, she said I might bring what I liked - whether stolen or not she would buy it.</p>
